## Never do                    # survives compaction only if also in VISION.md
- Disable failing tests — always file as an escalation instead.
- Modify CI config without human approval.
- Touch <protected paths, e.g. src/payments/ or src/billing/> (see permissions).
- Merge/deploy/change dependencies without the human approval gate.

